{"tid":632888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平第三度申請保釋　增加兩物業作抵押","createTime":"2018-04-17T21:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T07:18:22.000Z","uid":147314,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"45dcb29d74e02d4570adb1a18941a0ba3fbd21bf","tid":632888,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T21:37:37.000Z","msg":"何志平第三度申請保釋　增加兩物業作抵押<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1391741_1_L_20180418025140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1391741_1_L_20180418025140.jpg&h=6210c97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何志平第三度申請保釋，增加兩物業作抵押。（美聯社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局前局長何志平涉嫌行賄，目前在美國還押候審。何志平的代表律師向紐約法庭提交文件，第三度要求保釋。<br />\n<br />\n何志平一方提出增加抵押品作保釋，包括母親及家人合共價值400萬美元的香港物業。律師又提出，要求撤銷8項控罪的其中6項控罪。<br />\n<br />\n法官暫定將案件在11月5日審訊。68歲的何志平被控行賄非洲官員及洗黑錢，他自去年11月被捕後，一直關押在紐約曼哈頓下城區的懲教中心。何志平被指代表一間總部設於上海的中國能源公司，分別向乍得和烏干達的政府高層，提供賄款，並同時被控洗黑錢罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391741-20180418.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391741-20180418.htm&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74PgzmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=3f06fd22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391741-20180418.htm&h=fe4d7c93\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391741-20180418.htm</a>"},{"pid":"24b58f8f70175a1199a741a9d66300375b0c9a0e","tid":632888,"uid":132859,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T21:47:15.000Z","msg":"為咗保釋差唔多要變賣家產<br />\n好明顯一走就冇回頭著草啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你咪撚走添阿<br />\n咪又搞到香港人以後去美國俾人周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐成世啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e54275eacb787406